{"tid":2493322,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟講兩句 想時間快啲過 (115)","createTime":"2021-04-17T20:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T01:06:25.000Z","uid":304074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7535929868193c9a5b370e136fd75491cef1b12b","tid":2493322,"uid":304074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T20:50:23.000Z","msg":"依個post係俾失眠 失戀 想吐苦水 傾心事嘅人圍爐吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝一直以來喺post陪過我 俾過意見我嘅咁多位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個post 除咗係圍爐取暖 <br />\n大家都可以入嚟吹下水 發下癲<br />\n分享一下去嗰邊 做咗啲乜嘢 <br />\n除咗擺低自己心事 都可以散播正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩開心野想分享都可以返嚟㗎<br />\nPost 100 樓豬將個名單大改咗 <br />\n好耐無見嘅舊人歡迎返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n躲兒！牙麥！Followme！Cylmomt！靚柔公主！<br />\n塵埃！Gary！擱淺！旅行！牙堅！洞丸！牙姫！<br />\n牙娉！金太！毒計！離巴！牙喬！牙讀！中薯！<br />\nOral！牙朗！本澤馬！貓狗！雪花非花！風絲！<br />\n教授！投水！牙pui！牙空！牙敗！腸仔！芽菜！<br />\n牙白！牙晴！牙靖！牙吳！蓋蓋！牙門！牙石！<br />\n牙智！牙太！牙林！牙秒！牙柒！未準備好！<br />\n清瘡！牙波！仲有好多位！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗚 越來越多人唔係記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你成日留名 但係我唔記得加你個名嘅話對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨便插嘴is okay<br />\n依度無規矩的 free~<br />\n當然發表意見要考慮對方感受啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b7eb3b443e082ab065c89485e5110ea6988de0","tid":2493322,"uid":326957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T20:50:30.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"eaf5a66af6235242110a143636d85f76ea4b2181","tid":2493322,"uid":207799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T20:50:34.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"cb01f25a23055c4126dbcb182106c3d8535da855","tid":2493322,"uid":326957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T20:50:43.000